originalText.text: Chill Will from the Eastside is one of the best Djs ever. We hired him to DJ our baby shower and he was amazing.  He truly made our celebration unforgettable.  I cannot emphasize how polite and accommodating he was.  He arrived early to create a perfect set up and was exceptionally professional and super attentive.  He did a great job with intros and announcements throughout the night.  We highly recommend DJ Chill Will

originalText.text: I went from playing his mix tapes on my black Casio boom box, to only hiring him for ANY AND ALL of my events. He is the best of the best. Knows how to get your event popping and so very down to earth. It speaks volumes to his character! Very professional yet so humble. If u want ur event to be top notch, he's ur man! Can't wait for him to DJ my wedding in April!

Favorite street legend mix tape master .
